arts.ttl: Championship talking points: Lampard's Coventry sparkle, Millwall's steel and Boro stay perfect
arts.sum: Prior to the game, Cifuentes spoke of a need for reinforcements as the window draws to a close - that need did not change despite bouncing back from a loss at Preston to win in the Championship. Bristol City boss Gerhard Struber made little effort to hide where he wants to strengthen before the transfer window closes after watching his side gradually cede momentum to drop two late points at Derby on Friday.
